One of the reasons for the success of the Elegant Universe is undoubtedly that in the search for a unified physical theory, it is not a boring story.
Physicists have solved the fundamental problem between two key theories (for at the moment our universe is de facto divided into two worlds with different laws) and solve it so imaginatively that it is worth retelling even to lay people.
